<h2>New Seller Registration</h2>

<p>A new vendor has registered on Piessang Marketplace.</p>

<ul>
  <li><strong>Vendor name:</strong> <%= vendorName %></li>
  <li><strong>Contact email:</strong> <%= contactEmail %></li>
  <li><strong>Phone:</strong> <%= contactPhone %></li>
  <li><strong>Base location:</strong> <%= baseLocation %></li>
  <li><strong>Category:</strong> <%= categoryTitle %></li>
  <% if (subCategory) { %>
    <li><strong>Sub category:</strong> <%= subCategory %></li>
  <% } %>
  <li><strong>User UID:</strong> <%= uid %></li>
</ul>

<p style="margin-top: 16px;">
The seller account has been activated and seller access is now enabled.
</p>
